snippet.title: Shadow Warrior - Viscera Cleanup Detail Trailer
snippet.description:
Viscera Cleanup Detail is a standalone mini-game in which you play as the janitor from Zilla Enterprises responsible for cleaning up the mess made after everyone's been killed by Lo Wang.
